For those who choose to play it the way it's intended, Rykas will only talk to you at 51.  Without Rykas or a spoiler, you'll never know about Askot, Walnan or Akkstaff.  Thus, technically, you have to be 51+ to start the farming for the junk you should've been able to learn about in the levels they'd give you XP for.<br>
