You wouldn't know that you need quillmane until you were able to go into the PoA quest hall and talk with Solstin and that's 46 minimum.  (Not sure if that one follows with the 51 requirement as well)  (That alone should make quillmane a mob for Planes capable players since you don't learn about it until then.)<br>
